Nenek!

00:12:52.160 --> 00:12:54.000
Tunggu tunggu.

00:12:54.280 --> 00:12:55.440
Selamat Holi!

00:12:55.520 --> 00:12:58.960
Selamat Holi!  - Selamat Holi!

